source:
TEXT_BANKJN604_03000_SEQ_00<tab>Zukin is a Kojin with a new purpose for old chests.

※Please note that the difficulty of this quest has been synced to your current level. Furthermore, you may not proceed with a class or job that is different from when you accepted this quest.
target:
TEXT_BANKJN604_03000_SEQ_00<tab><var 48 F201FC /var><var 49 F201FD /var> Schwierigkeitsanpassung (Job/Klasse darf nicht gewechselt werden)<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var>

Zukin hat eine neue Verwendung für Schatztruhen gefunden.

source: TEXT_BANKJN604_03000_TODO_00<tab>Inspect octopus traps near the <var 1A 02 /var>Adventure<var 1A 01 /var> and obtain an octopus.
TEXT_BANKJN604_03000_TODO_01<tab>Deliver the giant koromo octopus to Zukin.

TEXT_BANKJN604_03000_ZUKIN_000_000<tab>We had some old treasure chests that were lying around, gathering dust. With some creativity on my part, I was able to convert them into octopus traps. And they work exceptionally well, if I may say so myself.
target: TEXT_BANKJN604_03000_ZUKIN_000_000<tab>Leere Schatztruhen sind doch viel zu schade zum Wegwerfen, also haben wir etwas herumgetüftelt und sie zu Oktopus-Fallen<var 1D /var>...... umgebaut!

source: TEXT_BANKJN604_03000_ZUKIN_000_001<tab>Now, I've a mind to gift the good folk of Kokajiya with a fresh catch, and I should be grateful if you could go out and inspect the traps.
target: TEXT_BANKJN604_03000_ZUKIN_000_001<tab>Die funktionieren so gut, dass wir damit mehr als genug Oktopusse fangen. Deshalb wollen wir einen davon dem Kokajiya schenken. Kannst du in den ausgelegten Fallen nachsehen, ob sich darin Beute verfangen<var 1D /var>...... hat?

source: TEXT_BANKJN604_03000_ZUKIN_000_002<tab>I've laid three over by the wreck southwest of here. One is bound to have caught an octopus by now. My thanks in advance, <var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var>.
target: TEXT_BANKJN604_03000_ZUKIN_000_002<tab><var 2B ((<var 32 ((EObj)) 03F61EA83A030502 /var>)) /var> haben wir bei dem Schiffswrack südwestlich von hier<var 1D /var>...... ausgelegt. Kontrolliere sie bitte, und bring mir einen möglichst großen Koromo-Oktopus.

source: TEXT_BANKJN604_03000_SYSTEM_000_011<tab>There is a mess of writhing tentacles in the chest!
TEXT_BANKJN604_03000_ZUKIN_000_020<tab>Ah, there you are. Did the kami bless us with a catch?
target: TEXT_BANKJN604_03000_ZUKIN_000_020<tab><var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var>! Hast du <var 32 ((EventItem)) 03F61E8DF7020502 /var> in unseren Fallen<var 1D /var>...... gefunden?

source: TEXT_BANKJN604_03000_ZUKIN_000_021<tab>Oho, such a large and lively octopus! Our blacksmith friends shall be pleased!
target: TEXT_BANKJN604_03000_ZUKIN_000_021<tab>Oh ja, schön frisch und lecker! So große Exemplare kriegt man nur selten zu<var 1D /var>...... Gesicht! Die Leute vom Kokajiya werden sich<var 1D /var>...... freuen.

source: TEXT_BANKJN604_03000_ZUKIN_000_023<tab>By the way, did I mention that older chests wreathed in weeds make the best traps? Well, they do. You may wish to remember this for your future reference.
target: TEXT_BANKJN604_03000_ZUKIN_000_023<tab>Ich habe den Eindruck, dass Koromo-Oktopusse bevorzugt in alte, mit Algen bewachsene Schatztruhen<var 1D /var>...... kriechen. Vielleicht hilft dir das Wissen beim nächsten Kontrollgang.
